=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex4 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral noisy sound, with noise oscillator character around 872 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: noisy
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 872.4062
  harmonic_decay_rate: -4.9944
  harmonic_regularity: 0.6210
  pitch_clarity: 18.3394
  inharmonicity: 0.2488
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -24.0956
  resonance_freq: 796.7285

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 4
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
